WEBVTT

00:02.134 --> 00:04.125
Previously on The Vampire Diaries:

00:04.303 --> 00:07.534
For over a century,
I have lived in secret, until now.

00:07.773 --> 00:10.003
I know the risk, but I have to know her.

00:10.175 --> 00:11.369
What are you?

00:11.543 --> 00:14.011
- I'm a vampire.
- You said you don't kill to survive.

00:14.179 --> 00:15.544
Animal blood keeps me alive.

00:15.714 --> 00:17.978
- But not as strong as Damon.
- Hello, brother.

00:18.150 --> 00:20.311
- Damon.
- Stefan finally fessed up.

00:20.486 --> 00:21.851
Stay away from me.

00:22.021 --> 00:24.353
That necklace contains an herb
called vervain.

00:24.523 --> 00:27.686
- It protects you from being compelled.
- I will keep your secret.

00:27.860 --> 00:29.828
But I can't be with you, Stefan.

00:30.329 --> 00:32.593
- What is that?
- A very important crystal.

00:32.798 --> 00:36.165
- Are you psychic or clairvoyant?
- Technically, Grams says I'm a witch.

00:36.335 --> 00:40.567
There was a time when this town
was very much aware of vampires.

00:40.806 --> 00:43.274
- Five bodies all drained of blood?
- They've come back.

00:45.444 --> 00:47.071
You just don't wanna die, do you?

00:47.312 --> 00:48.540
She's transitioning.

00:48.747 --> 00:49.873
- Into what?
- A vampire.

00:50.082 --> 00:52.710
- I don't know what's wrong with her.
- She'll be fine.

00:53.419 --> 00:55.080
- We'll all be fine.
- Vicki.

00:55.320 --> 00:58.483
I'll make sure that she does not hurt
anybody, Elena. I promise you.

00:59.124 --> 01:00.989
- All right, later, man.
- See you, bro.

